"tid":2415881,"uid":392982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T19:09:04.000Z","msg":"日本<br />\n<br />\n但交通規則執得好嚴,　一旦犯規被交通警捉到,　罰得好重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"超速捉得鬆手過香港<br />\n反而違泊就捉得超緊..<br />\n<br />\n不過日本咁多車場無藉口唔入場啦<br />\n求其路邊都有自動化爛地場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"果d唔算爛地"},{"pid":"b1ed1839724375bd4abe7328fab90a7bfb02f165","tid":2415881,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e106f58dbf847e9bf54f73d92deede4f549475f5","tid":2415881,"uid":280867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89459503ec55aec4fce72eb7bbc9fa487cbc7fbd","tid":2415881,"uid":340155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"新西蘭同埋加拿大都好正，<br />\n可以考慮吓租返架camper van，真係好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"新西蘭超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸車風景勁靚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"但係條路好直，好易恰眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2816c355771be56f30ac7964806b32b857d5993f","tid":2415881,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"美帝"},{"pid":"5462d9a19a6f264eed80d158a3e51fc23ab7c1b8","tid":2415881,"uid":289214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"回憶返D自駕過嘅地方<br />\n日本（沖繩 / 九州 / 關西 / 關東 / 北陸 / 東北 / 北海道等），最鍾意無PLANNING路過D大商店就咁鏟入去，就算大牌子好多時都有平野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣（高雄 / 墾丁），好多電單車，好似有堆蟻咁，交車時CUT唔到入車場，停一邊叫職員幫手先CUT到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泰國（布吉），當年未有GOOGLE MAP / GPS，問路就咁開玻璃問旁邊D電單車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法國（里昂），無乜特別，剩係記得D車開得好快，開百三四都係係咁俾人過頭，條路本身行80。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國（蘇格蘭），最鍾意呢度，風景靘，有時有鹿喺旁邊跳過（都有好多鹿車死左），夜晚抻手不見五指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冰島（環島），POINT TO POINT 最才兩三個鐘，得我一個揸都幾辛苦，回程由朝揸到晚十幾個鍾。不過好多體驗，雪山勁大風、踩雪堆等人救、差少少無油&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：冰島 &gt; 蘇格蘭 &gt; 日本"},{"pid":"274970b3dd36c858126ee14793c4550acb65c1d3","tid":2415881,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"051bfcc14aed9a5b13d5461b7dc741eaa33cbc3a","tid":2415881,"uid":392982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T19:09:04.000Z","msg":"日本<br />\n<br />\n但交通規則執得好嚴,　一旦犯規被交通警捉到,　罰得好重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:34:36.000Z","msg":"比人捉超速，見到係遊客：<br />\nToo fast, slower"},{"pid":"68c6f7b4431127bb058d4903b951b8d58cf82645","tid":2415881,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"北美 個條highway正撚到 個景靚撚到"},{"pid":"4d7877283303cb0692f8d343fa74f46057601d2e","tid":2415881,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e83acaf7616c4e6fcefa166c78934e70199e92ec","tid":2415881,"uid":339053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5e67d6369f15b39e1c4684bd063d4ccf8c6ea4a","tid":2415881,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769e8d33d8b50e814eeba87b119b74032957b89e","tid":2415881,"uid":26766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"日本真係爽到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"日本堅正。又少相機。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"唔算小啦，不過多數都大大隻字提你<br />\n自動速度陰蒂機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"試過俾老懚紅藍燈閃，Mark X 黎，我收慢佢就走左去"},{"pid":"ad1e74cc191aa1b87065f8cf906650e6e5ea0799","tid":2415881,"uid":44117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"澳洲 紐西蘭 日本 台灣 冰島 美國 中東 都ok<br />\n歐洲就一般 離開市區就好 市區難泊車or貴 撘火車已經夠"},{"pid":"10bc0f5b6dcfa209c3f09ea80b7292442ef9e933","tid":2415881,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:44:14.000Z","msg":"蒙古，揸成個月都係一望無際嘅地方 , 又唔使煩泊車"},{"pid":"a30c5699c08a0bffda056b02a6c3bdfe32ceecc9","tid":2415881,"uid":327271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"美國<br />\nRoad trip/飛車一流<br />\n冇咩鏡頭捉超速<br />\n係間唔中有一兩架警車埋伏<br />\n冇警察=冇speed limit<br />\n夜晚飛interstate成條路都係你"},{"pid":"9f370edc4cad4884767f96c2c3543950f711234a","tid":2415881,"uid":61257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭<br />\n澳洲"},{"pid":"75c76f97b8d874811ab5d23dfd25ab4bd457d6db","tid":2415881,"uid":275570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a30c5699c08a0bffda056b02a6c3bdfe32ceecc9","tid":2415881,"uid":327271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"美國<br />\nRoad trip/飛車一流<br />\n冇咩鏡頭捉超速<br />\n係間唔中有一兩架警車埋伏<br />\n冇警察=冇speed limit<br />\n夜晚飛interstate成條路都係你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n<br />\n去過4次美國,次次周鳩圍揸好正<br />\n<br />\n另揸英法西日澳紐,都係美國最正"},{"pid":"e01f864e490f6dcd10c1742b04cd1c0e88f85c65","tid":2415881,"uid":38305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4601eaa548eeae5710c8c599fd791f434da598dc","tid":2415881,"uid":30351,"like":7,"dislike":26,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"曾經試過係巴黎租車自駕<br />\n入凱旋門個迴旋處真係永世難忘<br />\ncls 六至八條行車線咁闊<br />\n但完全無劃線<br />\n乜尻車有<br />\n長時間都係咁多車<br />\n但又個個可以安全出入<br />\n<br />\n係香港<br />\n見啲人拗黎拗去迴旋轉要點行<br />\n真係得啖笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"隧道多到痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuVqbvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuVqbvL.jpg&h=e9df300b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae9453cb9a06bafe7366a0d68d425e1023aba283","tid":2415881,"uid":165058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"歐洲<br />\n1) 克羅地亞split --&gt; 薩拉熱窩--&gt; 黑山共和國--&gt; Dubrovnik, 風景 一流, 就算食露天餐廳 價錢都平.<br />\n2) 芬蘭<br />\n3) 德國 去奧地利上楚格峰 啤酒節 , 本來同朋友兩個人揸 但係佢竟然喺飛機上面唔見咗國際車牌, 結果全程得我一個人drive足全程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n4) 冰島全島遊14天<br />\n<br />\n5) 愛爾蘭北愛爾蘭 之後飛去 再租車去高地<br />\n<br />\n日本 <br />\n北海道,九州, 鹿兒島 沖繩, 四國加小豆島, etc. 兩年前十月一 到埗 日本打風, 第日上去上高地竟然好天. <br />\n仲有得 北陸四大節祭, 日日－去到酒店就去 條街 霸位.<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭南島, 風景我覺得靚過 冰島, 租一架十四座,七個朋友一齊去"},{"pid":"40a9b5065a6463cb8dc72a32d0f8716991f84867","tid":2415881,"uid":165058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"oh 仲有泰國曼谷去芭提雅 , 做乜特別<br />\n<br />\n台灣 台中去墾丁 經花蓮再去台北, 如果 係一個中途站早 出發有三分鐘就會遇上意外, 死左了."},{"pid":"b01c51e5656a3d4dde4a60fdec576527dcd84a6d","tid":2415881,"uid":195350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"冷門d<br />\n富國島"},{"pid":"796d8af6551724caae4d0b1aa86dc26835a27395","tid":2415881,"uid":34222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"跟過德國朋友自駕去國王湖 天鵝堡<br />\nHighway上到180 都比隔離車過哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bf266b4388649b0f58661b105d147cc721f52c","tid":2415881,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1a2f7d30fbcb85e00f15d1d351508be48f8ede14","tid":2415881,"uid":79410,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"揸過 <br />\n大陸(我都係去D 3-4線城市揸, 路好闊, 不過成日俾貨車推)<br />\n台灣(D 人揸車係癲, 我行慢線都推我, 砵我)<br />\n沖繩(幾好FEEL, 路靚又闊, D 人好有禮貎, 不過可能個個都係遊客)<br />\n沙巴(去咗5日, 未聽過有車砵過一聲, 夜晚神山冇車開高燈, 對面如有車嚟到佢會即刻開高燈射返你, 你較返低燈, 佢又會即刻較返低燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<