0Z","msg":"高速冇人跟錶"},{"pid":"6eb3cc8f3e336cf1e6bb176c0d63a2e618c48785","tid":2415881,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a2f7d30fbcb85e00f15d1d351508be48f8ede14","tid":2415881,"uid":79410,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"揸過 <br />\n大陸(我都係去D 3-4線城市揸, 路好闊, 不過成日俾貨車推)<br />\n台灣(D 人揸車係癲, 我行慢線都推我, 砵我)<br />\n沖繩(幾好FEEL, 路靚又闊, D 人好有禮貎, 不過可能個個都係遊客)<br />\n沙巴(去咗5日, 未聽過有車砵過一聲, 夜晚神山冇車開高燈, 對面如有車嚟到佢會即刻開高燈射返你, 你較返低燈, 佢又會即刻較返低燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n泰國(冇乜感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n澳洲(路大又長好易黑眼訓, CUT 線打燈個個都會讓你)<br />\n<br />\n沖繩, 沙巴, 澳洲 都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"澳洲日本無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef5ad5a683343d225fb90e660985c8e419d2dad","tid":2415881,"uid":139200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"自己渣過 <br />\n德國 英國 波蘭 法國 比利時 葡萄牙<br />\n日本 台灣 澳洲 <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得 日本 最好<br />\n自己渣過 關東 關西 北陸<br />\n基本上 無咩人唔跟規矩<br />\n又禮讓 超少少 無cam又無咩捉<br />\n泊車算方便 GPS又準<br />\n<br />\n歐洲 德國唔洗講啦<br />\n其他都基本上ok<br />\n但普遍超速罰得超金... <br />\n通常一張$600-700 港紙 (平國家平d la)<br />\n英國違泊 好似有極速交有半價<br />\n果邊渣車的人基本上都經驗唔錯<br />\n車品都唔算太閪 <br />\n除左你亂攝 搞親人之類啦<br />\n問題 都係自己超速 違泊 罰得金<br />\n<br />\n澳洲 都唔錯 都係 超速 同 違泊 罰得金<br />\n<br />\n台灣 就低能的 限速超低<br />\nd人渣車又有亂cut<br />\n仲要好多電單車 好危險下"},{"pid":"9e55e2ac0e02b434ec812df45a123166d10f26e1","tid":2415881,"uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"肯豆"},{"pid":"1a2f1988927118e3a51facfe66d9a659f64e8b61","tid":2415881,"uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e55e2ac0e02b434ec812df45a123166d10f26e1","tid":2415881,"uid":384355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"肯豆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"亞"},{"pid":"dc94a87dda6a03a3effe9e78300b91ae65eb21d6","tid":2415881,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"051bfcc14aed9a5b13d5461b7dc741eaa33cbc3a","tid":2415881,"uid":392982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T19:09:04.000Z","msg":"日本<br />\n<br />\n但交通規則執得好嚴,　一旦犯規被交通警捉到,　罰得好重"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"有次唔覺意喺差館面前衝咗黃燈<br />\n佢截停我<br />\n知我遊客都放我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03d0bda8a8f37b63eb4516895f68d8fe90e24d5","tid":2415881,"uid":339053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7352f9ba64878030cf0c713c88014ccfc3cd39eb","tid":2415881,"uid":340155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f90c202688a7714c40ecd9835b90b261f02ebcc","tid":2415881,"uid":339053,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89459503ec55aec4fce72eb7bbc9fa487cbc7fbd","tid":2415881,"uid":340155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"新西蘭同埋加拿大都好正，<br />\n可以考慮吓租返架camper van，真係好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"渣過幾次Ottawa-Vancouver 來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我嗰時由溫哥華出發渣camper van，去到渥太華就換返細車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"第一次揸Ottawa - Vancouver係揸部Integra<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後幾次揸架4Runner，舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好鐘意road trip，我唔介意揸車。<br />\n泰國揸過曼谷-布吉-芭堤雅-曼谷<br />\n9日揸咗3400km"},{"pid":"d698a80c23e3bd3868563ebcc379df106b4ed7b8","tid":2415881,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-2